    {BOLD}──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────{W}
    {BOLD}NOTATION CONVENTIONS{W}
    {BOLD}──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────{W}

      bps       Basis points. 1 bps = 0.01% = 1e-4
      RT        Round-trip (entry + exit fee combined)
      P30       30th percentile of the empirical distribution
      OOS       Out-of-sample
